works.description: The latest from the design house of Swiss car visionary Frank M. Rinderknecht is the BamBoo concept, which is just as unique as the company’s other concepts that are showcased at the Geneva Motor Show. The Rinspeed BamBoo, which the company calls a grown-up golf cart, is powered by electricity and will be showcased at the next Geneva Motor Show, which runs from March 3rd through 13th, 2011.
